{"tid":544815,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《溏心3》結局收視創30.8點新高！！","createTime":"2018-01-30T02:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T02:27:37.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a14490c7019e03d67d8ebc175b8cd43a6ba81ac6","tid":544815,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"【硬推「輪迴點擊」計算法】《溏心3》結局收視創30.8點新高 今晚搞慶功 <br />\n《溏心風暴3》有得搞慶功？！係呀，冇搞錯呀。<br />\n雖然《溏心3》開播以來收視同口碑都麻麻地，但無綫早前棄用CSM(中國廣視索福瑞媒介研究有限公司)及Kantar Media計法，疑為咗谷大條數，寧願用番舊嘅Nielsen計法，令好耐冇見過「3」字頭收視終於現曙光。<br />\n之前《誇世代》第50集大結局，<span style=\"color: red;\">以7日重溫之「輪迴點擊」收視方法計算</span>，有29.5點，以一收視點觀眾人數係65,150，即有約190萬人次。而據無綫最新公布嘅收視報告，1月19日播出《溏心3》第40集大結局，成績更上一層樓，有30.8點，約200萬人次。難怪無綫要大肆慶祝一下，今晚會喺將軍一間酒樓搞慶功宴，李司棋、夏雨、關菊英、岑麗香、黃翠如、阮兆祥等都會出席。"},{"pid":"bd6a59792c06f98eb357fee50951522e7f07524e","tid":544815,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a820731a054c4d7c703c8d679e68ad1950dc9389","tid":544815,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3683cb70ca1360d4eba19571fbf0a1b12065ebe","tid":544815,"uid":9395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"即係無限重溫都計？"},{"pid":"56c2ee93e0361e5695ee104dcefdc0111f3ecdc7","tid":544815,"uid":30040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e3683cb70ca1360d4eba19571fbf0a1b12065ebe","tid":544815,"uid":9395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"即係無限重溫都計？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"Click足7日當收視率 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b1bfab1e39ce7aeb2a3fdb00c3377b5514da85","tid":544815,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:27:37.0